CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 17, 1952, pg. 17 reads: "Christened - Friends and relatives gathered in home of Mr. and Mrs. Nathaniel Jackson to celebrate the christening of little Deborah Washington, which marks the fourth generation of the Jackson family. Mrs. Annie Jackson, great-grandmother; Mrs. Julia Hayes, grandmother; Mrs. Barbara Washington, mother, and little Morris Washington, brother. - Harris PHoto."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Barbara Washington, holding Deborah Washington, wearing christening outfit; Annie Jackson, and Julia Hayes holding Morris Washington, seated in home of Mr. and Mrs. Nathaniel Jackson for christening
